Google / GitHub OAuth
--------------------
Bundled OAuth client IDs/secrets in this repository are empty by
design. Platform account sign-in uses the optional BASE_API browser
flow. GitHub skill OAuth requires contributors to register their own
OAuth App (see config/github-oauth-defaults.ts).
